Params: {2: 'Chrome', 3: 'Time flies by so quickly in these kinds of places.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Did you often go to events like this before?', 3: '7'}
{2: 'Chrome', 3: 'Most of my previous outings were business-related social events. I rarely had chances like today to simply enjoy myself with friends.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Chrome', 3: "Of course! The atmosphere reminds me of F.O.S., especially walking side by side with you like this, it feels like we're back in our academy days.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Chrome', 3: 'You looked like you had fun today as well, I almost forgot you were the one who organized this festival.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Chrome', 3: "There's a tea room over there. Shall we sit down and have a chat?", 4: '1'}
